---
import Layout from '../../layouts/PostLayout.astro';

const title = 'CB Radio Voice Changer Teardown';
const description = 'Analysis and teardown of a CB radio voice changer module';
const pubDate = new Date('2025-10-06');
const tags = ['electronics', 'teardown', 'reverse-engineering', 'audio'];
const cost = '$5';
const manufacturer = 'Zuhai Jie Li (http://www.zh-jieli.com/)';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import voiceChangerImage from '../../assets/fixed/voice-changer/voice_changer_1.jpg';

const postData = {
    title,
    description,
    pubDate,
    tags,
    image: {
        url: voiceChangerImage.src
    },
    author: 'Your Name'
};

const IMAGE_PROPS = {
    loading: 'lazy',
    decoding: 'async',
    class: 'w-full h-auto rounded-lg',
    width: '100%',
    height: '100%',
    formats: ['avif', 'webp', 'jpg'],
    quality: 80,
    rotate: 0
};
---

<Layout frontmatter={postData}>
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <figure>
            <Image src={voiceChangerImage} alt="Voice Changer" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">Voice Changer</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium">Cost: {cost}</p>

        <h2>Manufacturer Information</h2>
        <p>According to an anonymous source: "The manufacturer is {manufacturer}. Many of their part numbers start with ACxxx."</p>
        <div class="note">
            <p>This particular part does not appear to have a publicly available datasheet.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Technical Details</h2>
        <div class="reference">
            <a href="https://electronics.stackexchange.com/a/491242" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                Reference: Identifying a JL chip in a Bluetooth device
            </a>
        </div>

        <h2>Experience Notes</h2>
        <p>During the first attempt, I examined an IC and attempted to bridge some of the gaps, which unfortunately resulted in frying the component.</p>

        <div class="note">
            <p>These components appear to vary significantly in their robustness. Some are much less tolerant of probing and modifications than others.</p>
        </div>

        <p>I'll need to acquire another unit to continue the analysis.</p>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .prose {
        max-width: 65ch;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    .note {
        background-color: #fffbeb;
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 1rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    .reference {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    .reference a {
        color: #3b82f6;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .reference a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>
